'''2013年索羅門群島地震'''是一起發生在當地時間2013年2月6日上午12點12分（[[UTC+11|UTC+11]]）的地震，震央位於[[索羅門群島|索羅門群島]]，規模8.0。此次地震的起因是[[印度-澳洲板塊|印度-澳洲板塊]]與[[太平洋板塊|太平洋板塊]]的碰撞，導致至少13人死亡，並引起1.5公尺高的[[海嘯|海嘯]]。

== 概況 ==
在當地時間2013年2月6日的12點12分（[[UTC|UTC]]1點12分），地震襲擊南[[太平洋|太平洋]]的索羅門群島<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/usc000f1s0#summary |title=M8.0 - 76km W of Lata, Solomon Islands 2013-02-06 01:12:27 UTC |publisher=Earthquake.usgs.gov |date= |accessdate=2013-02-10 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105160150/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/usc000f1s0#summary |dead-url=no }}</ref>震源深度28.7公里 (17.8 mi)，<ref name="bbc">{{cite news|date=2013-02-05|title=Powerful earthquake strikes off Solomon Islands|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2013-02-05|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-21347496|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021080924/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-21347496|dead-url=no}}</ref>震央在[[恩德島|恩德島]]的拉塔西方約76公里處，<ref name="autogenerated1"/>而原因是[[印度-澳洲板塊|印度-澳洲板塊]]和[[太平洋板塊|太平洋板塊]]擠壓。在主震發生前，曾出現數十起前震，<ref>{{cite report|publisher=[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]]|title=M8.0 - Santa Cruz Islands|accessdate=2013-02-05|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/usc000f1s0#summary|date=|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105160150/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/usc000f1s0#summary|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在發生規模8.0的主震後<ref>{{cite report|publisher=United States Geological Survey|title=M8.0 - Santa Cruz Islands|accessdate=2013-02-06|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/usc000f1s0#summary|date=|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105160150/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/usc000f1s0#summary|dead-url=no}}</ref>至少有20起餘震出現，<ref name="toi">{{cite news |agency=Agence France-Presse |date=2013-02-06 |title=Five dead as Solomons quake sparks Pacific tsunami |publisher=Times of India |accessdate=2013-02-06 |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/Five-dead-as-Solomons-quake-sparks-Pacific-tsunami/articleshow/18369309.cms |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130206205540/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/Five-dead-as-Solomons-quake-sparks-Pacific-tsunami/articleshow/18369309.cms |archivedate=2013-02-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>其中2月8日的一起規模達到7.1，<ref name=CNA-AFP-1253179>{{cite news |url= http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_asiapacific/view/1253179/1/.html |title= Villagers flee huge aftershock in tsunami-hit Solomon Islands |publisher= ChannelNewsAsia |author= AFP |date= 9 February 2013 |accessdate= 9 February 2013 |archive-date= 2013-02-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130216062959/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_asiapacific/view/1253179/1/.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>以及其他兩次餘震規模達7.0。<ref name="bbc"/>

== 海嘯 ==
[[太平洋海嘯警報中心|太平洋海嘯警報中心]]當時對[[索羅門群島|索羅門群島]]、[[巴布亞新幾內亞|巴布亞新幾內亞]]、[[斐濟|斐濟]]與其它鄰近地區的小島發布了海嘯警報，<ref>{{cite news|last=Vuibau|first=Tevita|title=Tsunami warning|url=http://www.fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=224546|accessdate=8 February 2013|newspaper=The Fiji Times|date=6 February 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130208011356/http://www.fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=224546|archive-date=2013-02-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>並且向[[澳洲|澳洲]]、[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]、[[印尼|印尼]]東部發布注意報。<ref name="wsj">{{cite news|author=Kaylene Hong|date=2013-02-05|title=Magnitude 8 Quake Strikes Off Santa Cruz Islands|publisher=[[新聞集團|新聞集團]]|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2013-02-05|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324445904578286703858134458.html|archive-date=2013-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528091141/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324445904578286703858134458.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="guard">{{cite news|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2013-02-05|title=Tsunami alert after Solomon Islands earthquake|accessdate=2013-02-05|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/feb/06/tsunami-alert-solomon-islands-earthquake|archive-date=2013-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130210125301/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/feb/06/tsunami-alert-solomon-islands-earthquake|dead-url=no}}</ref>最終地震所產生的海嘯高度在索羅門群島的拉塔約1公尺，<ref name="guard"/><ref name="wsj"/>並抵達島內500公尺的內陸，<ref name="toi"/>較小型的海嘯則分別在[[萬那杜|萬那杜]]與[[新喀里多尼亞|新喀里多尼亞]]出現11公分及50公分的高度。<ref name="abc">{{cite news|publisher=ABC Australia|date=2013-02-05|title=Solomons quake triggers tsunami, destroys villages|accessdate=2013-02-05|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-02-06/solomons-quake-triggers-tsunami/4504034|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107080211/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-02-06/solomons-quake-triggers-tsunami/4504034|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 損害 ==
在[[索羅門群島|索羅門群島]]的首都[[霍尼亞拉|霍尼亞拉]]，居民被指示往高處疏散，<ref name="guard"/>，引起交通混亂<ref name="abc"/>。當地媒體則報導四座村莊遭到摧毀。<ref name="toi"/>[[泰莫圖省|泰莫圖省]]東部則陷入洪水之中。<ref name="bbc"/>在[[恩德島|恩德島]]，1.5公尺的海嘯損毀了50間建築。<ref>{{cite news|agency=Associated Press|title=Tsunami damages dozens of homes in Solomon Islands|publisher=USAToday.com|accessdate=2013-02-05|date=2013-02-05|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/02/05/tsunami-warning-earthquake-south-pacific/1894875/|archive-date=2019-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624080417/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/02/05/tsunami-warning-earthquake-south-pacific/1894875/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在拉塔，海嘯破壞了機場設施並且淹沒低窪地區，<ref>{{cite news|title=Fears for villages after major quake hits near Solomons|publisher=Sydney Morning Herald|date=2013-02-06|accessdate=2013-02-05|url=http://www.smh.com.au/environment/fears-for-villages-after-major-quake-hits-near-solomons-20130206-2dxso.html|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014255/http://www.smh.com.au/environment/fears-for-villages-after-major-quake-hits-near-solomons-20130206-2dxso.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>使得9人死亡，包括5名年長者與1名小孩，<ref name="abc2"/>且超過100間房屋損毀，水力與電力皆處於中斷情況。<ref>{{cite news |first=Suzanne |last=McFadden |first2=Gerry |last2=Mullany |title=Tsunami Causes Deaths and Damages Homes on Solomon Islands |accessdate=2013-02-06 |date=2013-02-06 |newspaper=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/07/world/asia/earthquake-tsunami-solomon-islands-south-pacific.html |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014411/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/07/world/asia/earthquake-tsunami-solomon-islands-south-pacific.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>據報導在小村莊奈拉的所有房舍都被沖走，而另一村莊維加的房舍也被沖離原地。<ref>{{cite web |author=Updated at 9:53 pm on 7 February 2013 |url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/world/127442/airport-flood-hinders-tsunami-aid-effort |title=Radio New Zealand : News : World : Airport flood hinders tsunami aid effort |publisher=Radionz.co.nz |date= |accessdate=2013-02-10 |archive-date=2018-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180409233216/http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/world/127442/airport-flood-hinders-tsunami-aid-effort |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[努美阿|努美阿]]的官方對居民進行疏散，往[[新喀里多尼亞|新喀里多尼亞]]和[[洛亞蒂群島|洛亞蒂群島]]移動。<ref name="cnn">{{cite news|publisher=CNN|title=Powerful quake strikes in South Pacific, sparks tsunami|accessdate=2013-02-05|date=2013-02-05|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/02/05/world/asia/solomon-islands-quake/?hpt=hp_t1|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813081230/http://www.cnn.com/2013/02/05/world/asia/solomon-islands-quake/?hpt=hp_t1|dead-url=no}}</ref>居民也向[[斐濟|斐濟]]首都[[蘇瓦|蘇瓦]]的高地避難。<ref name="toi"/> 此次地震使得13人死亡，5人失蹤。<ref name="abc2">{{cite news|publisher=Fairfax New Zealand Limited|date=2013-02-07|title=Airport damage hits Solomons quake cleanup|author=Nicole Pryor And Agencies|accessdate=2013-02-07|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/south-pacific/8271293/Airport-damage-hits-Solomons-quake-cleanup|archive-date=2016-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204094559/http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/south-pacific/8271293/Airport-damage-hits-Solomons-quake-cleanup|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

